    {
      "id": "/page/0/Text/4",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">Like single-name barrier options, Altiplano options have two componentsâ€”a vanilla-type payoff if a barrier event occurs, and a coupon payoff if it does not. Usually the barrier event is to have at least one stock reach a predetermined barrier.</p>",
