    {
      "id": "/page/0/TextInlineMath/7",
      "block_type": "TextInlineMath",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"TextInlineMath\" class=\"has-continuation\">where <i>IB</i> is 1 if a barrier event in relation to barrier level <i>B</i> occurs, and is 0 if it does not, in which case the option would pay a coupon <i>C</i>. Here we have used a call option, but, in principle, we could</p>",
